overview: The 16th annual Tournament of Death took place June 10th, 2017. This tournament marked the debut Tournament of Death for John Wayne Murdoch, Shlak, G-Raver and Clint Margera. This is also the first mainstream Tournament of Death Jimmy Havoc competed in, having wrestled in ToD Europe as a member of Westside Xtreme Wrestling.
tagline: 9 Men Strive for Survival in the Bloodiest Afternoon in Wrestling
title: CZW Tournament of Death 16
